data.description: Charming fully remodeled ranch w/farmhouse accents throughout in established Oakdale. Close proximity to Uptown! Kitchen features soft close shaker cabinets, restored original farmhouse sink, granite countertops, SS appliances & brick backsplash. Spacious dining area w/updated lighting and farmhouse tile floor and beadboard ceiling. Refinished original hardwood floors. Primary bedroom has a fully remodeled en suite bathroom. Mud/laundry room w/beadboard ceiling/shiplap walls w/access to the spacious deck and backyard. The living room features hardwood floors, w/electric fireplace & french doors. Huge .8 acre lot that other structures could easily be added to. Circular driveway, shed, historic oak, pecan and fruit trees. Assumable loan for qualified buyers!
